stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> DAY_OFF
  DAY_OFF --> NIGHT_STANDBY: low light
  NIGHT_STANDBY --> MOTION_ACTIVE: motion detected
  MOTION_ACTIVE --> NIGHT_STANDBY: motion timeout
  NIGHT_STANDBY --> DAY_OFF: high light
  MOTION_ACTIVE --> MANUAL_OVERRIDE: remote command
  NIGHT_STANDBY --> MANUAL_OVERRIDE: remote command
  MANUAL_OVERRIDE --> NIGHT_STANDBY: override cleared
  DAY_OFF --> FAULT: sensor or system fault
  NIGHT_STANDBY --> FAULT: sensor or system fault
  MOTION_ACTIVE --> FAULT: sensor or system fault
  FAULT --> NIGHT_STANDBY: recovered
